Package org.bff.javampd.song

Class MPDSongDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bff.javampd.song.MPDSongDatabase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SongDatabase
    public class MPDSongDatabase
extends Object
implements SongDatabase
    MPDSongDatabase represents a song database controller to a MPD. To obtain an instance of the class you must use the MusicDatabase.getSongDatabase() method from the MPD connection class.
    Author:
    Bill
